            <title>[FLINK-2130] RabbitMQ source does not fail when failing to retrieve elements</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2130</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The RMQ source only logs when elements cannot be retrieved. Failures are not propagated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
